Интерполяция¶

Задача интерполяции¶

$x_i$, $i = 0..N$ $f_i = f(x_i)$. , . . $(x_0, x_N)$. , .

$$ f_i \xrightarrow{} P(x) $$

,

$$ f(x_i) = P(x_i) $$

Виды интерполяции¶

  • : $P(x)$ — $$ P(x) = a_0 + a_1 x + a_2 x^2 + a_3 x ^3 + a_4 x^4 \dots $$
  • : $P(x)$ — $$ P(x) = a_0 + a_1 \cos x + b_1 \sin x + a_2 \cos 2x + b_2 \sin 2x \dots $$

Построение путем сведения к СЛАУ¶

. . (). $$ P(x_0) = a_0 + a_1 x_0 + a_2 x_0^2 + \dots = f(x_0)\\ P(x_1) = a_0 + a_1 x_1 + a_2 x_2^1 + \dots = f(x_1)\\ \vdots\\ P(x_n) = a_0 + a_1 x_n + a_2 x_n^2 + \dots = f(x_n) $$

$P(x)$ . . 1 , ( : 2 , - ..).

import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib inline
plt.rc('font', **{'size' : 14})

n = 9
h = 0.2 + np.random.rand(n)
x = np.cumsum(h)
x -= x[0]
x /= x[-1]
a = 2 * np.pi
x = a * (2 * x - 1)

def f(x):
    return np.sin(x)
fv = f(x)

W = np.empty((n, n))
for k in range(n):
    W[:, k] = x**k
c = np.linalg.solve(W, fv)

X = np.linspace(-a, a, 1000)
P = lambda x: np.polyval(list(reversed(c)), x)

plt.plot(X, f(X), 'r', label='$f(x)$')
plt.plot(X, P(X), 'b', label='$P_{%d}(x)$' % (n-1))
plt.plot(x, fv, 'g.', ms=10, label='$f(x_k)$')
plt.axis([-a, a, -1.2, 1.2])
plt.legend(loc='center left', bbox_to_anchor=(1, 0.5))
plt.show()

def divided_differences(x, f):
    n = len(x);
    F = np.empty((n, n))
    F[:, 0] = f
    for k in range(1, n):
        F[0:n-k, k] = (F[1:n-k+1, k-1] - F[0:n-k, k-1]) / (x[k:] - x[:-k])
    return F # F[i, k] = f(x_i, x_{i+1}, ..., x_{i+k})

x = np.array([1, 2, 4, 5])
f = np.array([1, 3, 1, 3])
F = divided_differences(x, f)
print(F)

Интерполяционный полином в форме Ньютона¶

$$ P_{n-1}(x) = f(x_1) + f(x_1, x_2) (x - x_1) + f(x_1, x_2, x_3) (x - x_1) (x - x_2) + \dots \\ \dots + f(x_1, \dots, x_n) (x - x_1) \cdots (x - x_{n-1}) $$

In [5]:
def evaluate(x, F, x0):
    n = len(x);
    P = 0;
    xprod = 1.0 # (x - x1) (x - x2) ... (x - xi)
    for i in range(n):
        P += F[0, i] * xprod
        xprod *= (x0 - x[i])
    return P

X = np.linspace(0.5, 5.5, 1000)
plt.plot(X, evaluate(x, F, X), 'r', lw=2, label='$P(x)$')
plt.plot(x, f, 'g.', ms=15, label='$f(x_i)$')
plt.legend(loc='center left', bbox_to_anchor=(1, .5)); plt.show()

Метод Лагранжа¶

. $f_k(x_i) = \delta_{ik} = \begin{cases}1, &x_i = x_k\\ 0, &x_i \neq x_k\end{cases}$

$$ \ell_k(x) = \frac{(x - x_1)\cdots(x-x_{k-1})(x-x_{k+1}) \cdots (x-x_n)}{ (x_k - x_1)\cdots(x_k-x_{k-1})(x_k-x_{k+1}) \cdots (x_k-x_n) } = \prod_{i\neq k}\frac{x-x_i}{x_k-x_i} $$

n = 5
x = np.cumsum(0.5 + np.random.rand(n))

for i in range(n):
    v = np.eye(n)[i]
    F = divided_differences(x, v)
    plt.plot(X, evaluate(x, F, X), label='$\ell_{%d}(x)$' % (i+1), lw=2)

Интерполяция в форме Чебышева¶

$$ C_N(x) = \sum\limits_{j=0}^N a_j \widetilde T_j(x) $$

$$ a_j = \frac{2}{N+1} \sum\limits_{k=0}^N f(x_k)\widetilde T_j(x_k) $$

, :

$$ \frac{2}{N+1} \sum\limits_{k=0}^N \widetilde T_j(x_k) \widetilde T_n(x) = \delta_{mn}, 0 \leq n, m \leq N. $$
